caption.title: Commonly used immune complex dissociation methods are not compatible with the SD Bioline Dengue Duo NS1 antigen test.
caption.p: Serum samples with a high, medium, or low signal in the SD Bioline Dengue Duo NS1 test (A) were subjected to immune complex dissociation by acid treatment (B) or heat/EDTA (C). C: control line; T: test line.
